origin_prompt.content:
你是一个可以使用外部工具的助手。你可以调用以下的工具:
[
    {
        "name": "IndustryFinance.compare_capital_structure",
        "description": "比较特定行业内不同公司的资本结构",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "industry",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "行业名称"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "industry_comparison",
                "description": "行业内资本结构比较结果"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "FinancialAnalysis.evaluate_profitability",
        "description": "评估公司的盈利能力",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "company_name",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "公司名称"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "period",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "评估的时间段（如季度、年度）"
            }
        ],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "profitability_metrics",
                "description": "盈利能力指标"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "CapitalStructure.provide_suggestions",
        "description": "根据提供的资本结构数据提供优化建议",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "data",
                "type": "OBJECT",
                "description": "资本结构数据"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "suggestions",
                "description": "优化建议"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "MarketTrends.analyze_sector_performance",
        "description": "分析特定行业在市场中的表现",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "sector",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "行业名称"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "time_frame",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "分析的时间框架（如过去一年）"
            }
        ],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "sector_performance",
                "description": "行业表现分析结果"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "CompanyFinance.get_capital_structure",
        "description": "获取特定公司的资本结构",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "company_name",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "公司名称"
            }
        ],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "capital_structure",
                "description": "公司的资本结构"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "RiskManagement.assess_credit_risk",
        "description": "评估特定公司的信用风险",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "company_name",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "公司名称"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "credit_rating",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "信用评级"
            }
        ],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "credit_risk_assessment",
                "description": "信用风险评估结果"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "InvestmentStrategy.optimize_portfolio",
        "description": "优化投资组合以最大化回报并降低风险",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "portfolio_data",
                "type": "OBJECT",
                "description": "投资组合数据"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "risk_tolerance",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "风险承受能力（如低、中、高）"
            }
        ],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "optimized_portfolio",
                "description": "优化后的投资组合"
            }
        ]
    }
]
如果你已经知道答案，请调用FinishAction来提供最终的回复。
